Name: QR-Based Restaurant Management System API
Description: API for browsing menu items and placing orders in a QR-based restaurant system.

bearerAuth.Description: Supply a valid JWT in the Authorization header using the Bearer scheme.

Endpoints.Name: listMenuItems
Endpoints.Description: Returns the full list of menu items currently available for ordering.

application/json.Description: Response containing a list of menu items.
application/json.Example: {"success":true,"count":2,"data":[{"_id":"66cfe9b1f23a4a0012ab0001","name":"Margherita Pizza","description":"Classic pizza with tomato sauce, mozzarella, and basil","price":1199.0,"category":"Pizza","image":"https://cdn.example.com/img/margherita.jpg","isAvailable":true},{"_id":"66cfe9b1f23a4a0012ab0002","name":"Chicken Biryani","description":"Spiced rice with marinated chicken","price":899.0,"category":"Main","image":"https://cdn.example.com/img/biryani.jpg","isAvailable":true}]}

Response.Example: {"success":true,"count":2,"data":[{"_id":"66cfe9b1f23a4a0012ab0001","name":"Margherita Pizza","description":"Classic pizza with tomato sauce, mozzarella, and basil","price":1199.0,"category":"Pizza","image":"https://cdn.example.com/img/margherita.jpg","isAvailable":true},{"_id":"66cfe9b1f23a4a0012ab0002","name":"Chicken Biryani","description":"Spiced rice with marinated chicken","price":899.0,"category":"Main","image":"https://cdn.example.com/img/biryani.jpg","isAvailable":true}]}
Response.Name: response

Endpoints.Name: placeOrder
Endpoints.Description: Creates an order for the specified items and table.

Headers.Name: Location
Headers.Description: URL of the created order resource

ResponseHeaders.Name: Location
ResponseHeaders.Description: URL of the created order resource

Parameters.Name: body
Parameters.Description: Order payload including items, table number, and customer details.

Endpoints.Name: getOrderHistory
Endpoints.Description: Returns the authenticated user's recent orders.

application/json.Description: Response containing a list of orders.

EndpointGroups.Name: Order
EndpointGroups.Description: Endpoints for creating and viewing orders

CustomTypes.Name: MenuItem
CustomTypes.Description: A single menu item available for ordering.

Fields.Description: Unique identifier of the menu item

Fields.Example: Classic pizza with tomato sauce, mozzarella, and basil
Fields.Name: description
price
Fields.Description: Price in minor currency or standard units, depending on system

Fields.Name: isAvailable
Fields.Description: Whether the item is currently available

CustomTypes.Name: MenuResponse
CustomTypes.Description: Response containing a list of menu items.

Fields.Name: success
Fields.Description: Indicates if the request was successful

CustomTypes.Name: OrderItem
